name: Agigongnyong Dooly
overview: Agigongnyong Dooly, also known as The Dinosaur Dooley is a Sega Master System shoot-'em-up game released exclusively in South Korea. It is based on Dooly the Little Dinosaur, a Korean cartoon. Two versions exist - a Korean text version from 1991, and an English text version from 1993 that was cancelled.
